definition:
A man living at the time of Divided Monarchy, first mentioned at 2Ki.22.12; 
 son of: Micaiah (H4320); 
 father of: Elnathan (H0494K); also called Abdon at 2Ch.34.20; 
Also named: av.don (עַבְדּוֹן "Abdon" H5658K)
 § Achbor = "mouse"
1) father of king Baal-hanan of Edom
2) son of Michaiah and contemporary of king Josiah of Judah
